      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.qYA6qBtNgc7kydMP]{Divine Champion}</p>\n<p>Choose a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.SdlB9viiKckPr0LZ]{connection} (as per the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.Item.bItuvukGHbObTApr]{mystic} class feature) that fits within your deity’s ethos (subject to the GM’s discretion). Your bond with your deity has grown strong enough for you to duplicate the effects of some of the connection spells, though you don’t actually gain any connection abilities.</p>\n<p>Once per day, you can cast the 1st- or 2nd-level spell of your chosen connection as a spell-like ability. At 10th level, you can use this ability twice per day, and at 14th level, you can use this ability three times per day. The save DC of these spells is equal to 10 + the spell’s level + your key ability score modifier.</p>"
